OL,5,G1200 Inside the Ambulance: Coast and
OL,6,G     Country
OL,7,     FParamedics in Oxford race to an
OL,8,     F8-month-old baby who needs urgent
OL,9,     Fhelp to breathe. In Portsmouth, a
OL,10,     Fcancer patient thinks her
OL,11,     Fchemotherapy drugs are causing her
OL,12,     Fchest pain.
OL,13,G1300 Inside the Ambulance: Coast and
OL,14,G     Country
OL,15,     FToday, crews struggle to reach a
OL,16,     Fwoman who has fallen from her
OL,17,     Fhorse on treacherous boggy ground.
OL,18,     FParamedics also treat a
OL,19,     F14-year-old boy in agony with
OL,20,     Fsuspected appendicitis.
